usage: sifas_card_downloader [-h] [--organize] [--update] [--download]

searches and downloads SIFAS cards

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  --update    update the json file containing card data to reflect the current
              available cards in idol.st
  --download  download the cards
  --organize  organize downloaded cards in a directory per unit, then a
              subdirectory per idol